- ym   = session[:yearmonth]
- smno = session[:smno] || ym
.pl-6
  %hr/
  %table.tb.menu-table{border: "0", cellpadding: "0", cellspacing: "0"}
    %tr
      %td
        = link_to "取引先一覧", adlists_path, class: "btn wtext btn-info"
      - MenusHelper::GYO_LIST.each do |label, kanas|
        %td
          .dropdown
            %label.btn.btn-sm.btn-secondary{tabindex: "0"}= "#{label} ▾"
            %ul.dropdown-content.menu.bg-base-100.rounded-box.z-20.w-20.p-2.shadow.text-black{tabindex: "0"}
              - kanas.each do |kana|
                %li= link_to kana, adlists_path(gyo: kana)
      %td
        = link_to "船籍一覧", registries_path,  class: "btn wtext btn-info"
  %hr/
  .hoge
    %table.menu-table
      %tr
        %td{colspan: "8"}
          取引管理
          %span.TB12.text-blue-600.text-xs
            取引台帳の閲覧は、取引番号の一部(または全部)を入力してボタンをクリックするか、
            検索したい文字を入力してボタンをクリックします。
      %tr
        %td
          %span.TB12.text-blue-600.text-xs 取引番号
          %br/
          %form{method:"post", action: "#{orders_search_path}"}
            %input.box.input.input-bordered.border-2.border-neutral.bg-base-100{maxlength: "9", name: "keyword", size: "9", type: "text", style: "ime-mode:disabled;", value: "#{ym}"}/
            %br/
            %input.btn.wtext.btn-info{name: "submit", type: "submit", value: "取引番号"}/
            = hidden_field_tag('authenticity_token', form_authenticity_token)
        %td
          %span.TB12.text-blue-600.text-xs 取引番号
          %br/
          %form{method: "post", action: "#{orders_alllist_path}"}
            = hidden_field_tag('authenticity_token', form_authenticity_token)
            %input.input.input-bordered.border-2.border-neutral.bg-base-100{name: "SMNo", size: "10", style: "ime-mode:disabled;", type: "text", value: "#{smno}"}/
            %br/
            %input{name: "fixed", type: "hidden", value: "0"}/
            %input.btn.wtext.btn-info{type: "submit", value: "未受決分"}/
        %td
          %span.TB12.text-blue-600.text-xs 取引番号
          %br/
          %form{method: "post", action: "#{orders_alllist_path}"}
            = hidden_field_tag('authenticity_token', form_authenticity_token)
            %input.input.input-bordered.border-2.border-neutral.bg-base-100{name: "SMNo", size: "10", style: "ime-mode:disabled;", type: "text", value: "#{smno}"}/
            %br/
            %input{name: "fixed", type: "hidden", value: "1"}/
            %input.btn.wtext.btn-info{type: "submit", value: "受注決定分"}/
        %td
          %span.TB12.text-blue-600.text-xs 検索文字列
          %br/
          %form{method:"post", action: "#{orders_search_path}"}
            %input.box.input.input-bordered.border-2.border-neutral.bg-base-100{name: "keyword", size: "10", style: "ime-mode:disabled;", type: "text", value: ""}/
            %input{name: "keykind", type: "hidden", value: "etype"}/
            %br/
            %input.btn.wtext.btn-info{type: "submit", value: "形式検索"}/
            = hidden_field_tag('authenticity_token', form_authenticity_token)
        %td
          %span.TB12.text-blue-600.text-xs 検索文字列
          %br/
          %form{method:"post", action: "#{orders_search_path}"}
            %input.box.input.input-bordered.border-2.border-neutral.bg-base-100{name: "keyword", size: "10", style: "ime-mode:disabled;", type: "text", value: ""}/
            %input{name: "keykind", type: "hidden", value: "engno"}/
            %br/
            %input.btn.wtext.btn-info{type: "submit", value: "機番検索"}/
            = hidden_field_tag('authenticity_token', form_authenticity_token)
        %td
          %span.TB12.text-blue-600.text-xs 検索文字列
          %br/
          %form{method:"post", action: "#{orders_search_path}"}
            %input.box.input.input-bordered.border-2.border-neutral.bg-base-100{name: "keyword", size: "10", type: "text", value: ""}/
            %input{name: "keykind", type: "hidden", value: "shipname"}/
            %br/
            %input.btn.wtext.btn-info{type: "submit", value: "船名検索"}/
            = hidden_field_tag('authenticity_token', form_authenticity_token)
        %td
          %span.TB12.text-blue-600.text-xs 検索文字列
          %br/
          %form{method:"post", action: "#{orders_search_path}"}
            %input.box.input.input-bordered.border-2.border-neutral.bg-base-100{name: "keyword", size: "10", type: "text", value: ""}/
            %input{name: "keykind", type: "hidden", value: "company"}/
            %br/
            %input.btn.wtext.btn-info{type: "submit", value: "会社名検索"}/
            = hidden_field_tag('authenticity_token', form_authenticity_token)
        %td
          %span.TB12.text-blue-600.text-xs 検索文字列
          %br/
          %form{method:"post", action: "#{orders_search_path}"}
            %input.box.input.input-bordered.border-2.border-neutral.bg-base-100{name: "keyword", size: "30",maxlength: "30", type: "text", value: ""}/
            %input{name: "keykind", type: "hidden", value: "memo"}/
            %br/
            %input.btn.wtext.btn-info{type: "submit", value: "メモ検索"}/
            = hidden_field_tag('authenticity_token', form_authenticity_token)
    %hr{size: "3"}/
    %table.menu-table
      %tr
        %td{colspan: "5"}
          在庫管理
          %span.TB12.text-blue-600.text-xs
            入庫の入力は、在庫の一覧から該当部品をクリックするか、新規在庫の場合「入庫入力」から
            部品番号を指定します。Ａ部品表に無い部品の在庫登録もそこから行います。
      %tr
        %td
          %form{action: stocks_path}
            %span.TB12.text-blue-600.text-xs A部品コード
            %br/
            %input.input.input-bordered.border-2.border-neutral.bg-base-100{name: "partno", size: "9", maxlength: "9", style: "ime-mode:disabled; width: 8rem;", type: "text", value: ""}/
            %br/
            %input.tb1.btn.wtext.btn-info{type: "submit", value: "Ａ部品全在庫"}/
        %td
          %form{action: stocks_path}
            %span.TB12.text-blue-600.text-xs A部品コード
            %br/
            %input.input.input-bordered.border-2.border-neutral.bg-base-100{name: "partno", size: "9", maxlength: "9", style: "ime-mode:disabled; width: 8rem;", type: "text", value: ""}/
            %input{name: "in_stock", type: "hidden", value: "1"}/
            %br/
            %input.tb1.btn.wtext.btn-info{type: "submit", value: "Ａ部品在庫有り"}/
        %td
          %form{action: stockbs_path}
            %span.TB12.text-blue-600.text-xs B部品コード
            %br/
            %input.input.input-bordered.border-2.border-neutral.bg-base-100{name: "partno", size: "9", maxlength: "9", style: "ime-mode:disabled; width: 8rem;", type: "text", value: ""}/
            %br/
            %input.tb1.btn.wtext.btn-info{type: "submit", value: "Ｂ部品全在庫"}/
        %td
          %form{action: stockbs_path}
            %span.TB12.text-blue-600.text-xs B部品コード
            %br/
            %input.input.input-bordered.border-2.border-neutral.bg-base-100{name: "partno", size: "9", maxlength: "9", style: "ime-mode:disabled; width: 8rem;", type: "text", value: ""}/
            %input{name: "in_stock", type: "hidden", value: "1"}/
            %br/
            %input.tb1.btn.wtext.btn-info{type: "submit", value: "Ｂ部品在庫有り"}/
      %tr
        %td
          %form{action: "zaikonlist.asp"}
          %input.btn.wtext.btn-info{type: "submit", value: "Ａ在庫非表示リスト"}/
        %td
          %form{action: "norder.asp", method: "post"}
          %input.tb1.btn.wtext.btn-info{type: "submit", value: "Ａ部品注文"}/
        %td
          %input.btn.wtext.btn-info{type: "submit", value: "Ｂ在庫非表示リスト"}/
          %form{action: "hzaikonlist.asp"}
    %hr/
    %table.menu-table
      %tr
        %td{colspan: "4"}
          Ａ部品台帳
          %span.TB12.text-blue-600.text-xs
            Ａ部品台帳のメンテ（価格改定など）は、部品台帳を検索してからクリックし
            部品詳細を出力しその画面から実施します
      %tr
        %td
          %form{action: parts_path}
            %span.TB12.text-blue-600.text-xs A部品コード
            %br/
            %input.input.input-bordered.border-2.border-neutral.bg-base-100{name: "keyword", size: "9", maxlength: "9", style: "ime-mode:disabled; width: 8rem;", type: "text", value: ""}/
            %br/
            %input.tb1.btn.wtext.btn-info{title: "１．新潟標準部品 NDPからの Excel価格表データに存在する分", type: "submit", value: "Ａ部品"}/
        %td
          %form{action: "partslist.asp", method: "post"}
          %input.input.input-bordered.border-2.border-neutral.bg-base-100{name: "sNAME", size: "12", style: "ime-mode:disabled;", type: "text", value: ""}/
          %br/
